25|$|Campbell {{believed}} that from its foundation until 1980, Theosophy had gained {{tens of thousands}} of adherents. He noted that in that latter year, there were circa 35,000 members of the Adyar-based <b>Theosophical</b> <b>Society</b> (9000 of whom were in India), c.5,500 members of the <b>Theosophical</b> <b>Society</b> in America, c.1500 members of the <b>Theosophical</b> <b>Society</b> International (Pasadena), and about 1200 members of the United Lodge of Theosophy.|$|E
